Package com.atakmap.android.gui.drawable

Class ThreeStateDrawable

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.graphics.drawable.Drawable
      • com.atakmap.android.gui.drawable.ThreeStateDrawable
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CheckBoxDrawable, VisibilityDrawable
    public class ThreeStateDrawable
extends android.graphics.drawable.Drawable
    A drawable icon that has 3 states, typically ON, OFF, and SEMI Used for visibility toggles and checkboxes in Overlay Manager
